Media personality, Toke Makinwa has taken to her Twitter account to reveal what she did to a man she saw peeing by the road side. According to her, she body-shamed him and yelled at him to keep Lagos clean. “The guy peeing by the road side, I saw your willy, it’s like my little finger. I pulled my window down and yelled small peeenis keep Lagos clean. “He just casually brought out his instrument to water the ground, like no biggie I’m just going to pee for you to see,” she wrote. Source